   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>After 1931 Brother Watchman Nee led the church in Shanghai in a study of the Gospel of Matthew intermittently for several years.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>This volume consists of notes taken during those studies that were later edited and polished.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>It covers the interpretation from chapter one through chapter twenty-five, chapter by chapter and verse by verse in sequence, and includes the exposition of all important sections.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>The contents are exceedingly rich and multifaceted, with a rich supply of life and the light of the truth.</S>
   </TEXT>
